Name: Bubble Sort
Description:
"Also known as sinking sort, repeatedly stepping through list comparing "adjacent" elements and swapping if adjacent elements are out of order.

Name: Selection Sort
Description: "Sorts by repeatedly finding min elements and swapping with frontmost out of order element"

Name: Insertion Sort
Description: "Sorts by repeatedly moving out of order min elements to front of list while sustaining order"
